      "abstract": [
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "fr",
          "value": "L’objectif de l'étude était d'analyser le lien entre ce déterminant de santé et l’indice de masse corporelle (IMC) chez l’adolescent."
        },
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "The objective of the study was to analyse the relationship between this determinant of health and body mass index (BMI) in adolescents."
        }
